\mathbf{'\theta} \pm t_{(1-\alpha/2, n-p)} s \sqrt{\mathbf{'[\mathbf{F}(\hat{\theta})'\mathbf{F}(\hat{\theta})]^{-1}}}
\]\(t_{(1-\alpha/2, n-p)}\) critical value \(t\)-distribution \(n - p\) degrees freedom.\(s = \sqrt{\hat{\sigma^2}_\epsilon}\) estimated standard deviation residuals.Special Case: Single Parameter \(\theta_j\)focus single parameter \(\theta_j\), let \(\mathbf{'} = (0, \dots, 1, \dots, 0)\) (1 \(j\)-th position). , confidence interval \(\theta_j\) becomes:\[
