\]:\(\mathbf{s}_j = \hat{\theta}^{(j+1)} - \hat{\theta}^{(j)}\) (change parameters).\(\mathbf{y}_j = \nabla Q(\hat{\theta}^{(j+1)}) - \nabla Q(\hat{\theta}^{(j)})\) (change gradient).\(\mathbf{H}_j\) current inverse Hessian approximation.

